96
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:28,570
Nevíte, kde žije?

97
00:06:28,570 --> 00:06:30,120
Nemá stálou adresu.

98
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:33,340
Chodí do agentury práce

99
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:34,880
a sotva se uživí.

100
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,940
